  "prompt": "Is there a way to sort by the most upvoted answers on Quora?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, Quora does not have a built-in feature that allows users to sort answers by the number of upvotes directly. However, answers are typically displayed in a way that the most upvoted answers appear at the top of the list by default.\n\nIf you're looking for highly upvoted answers, you can simply browse through the answers provided for a particular question, and the ones with the most upvotes will usually be positioned first. \n\nFor the most accurate and updated information, you may want to check the Quora platform directly or consult their help section.",
